  <h1>Privacy Policy - TopNotch Mobile</h1>
  <p>Effective Date: September 2025</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We collect the following information from users of TopNotch Mobile:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Name and email address (for account creation and authentication via Google login)</li>
    <li>Pet information (for managing your pet's profile and services)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>Your information is used solely to provide and improve our services, including:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Account management and login authentication</li>
    <li>Personalized pet care features</li>
    <li>Communications about your account and service updates</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell your data. Your information may be shared with trusted third-party services only for:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Authentication (Supabase, Google login)</li>
    <li>Service functionality required to provide app features</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. User Rights</h2>
  <p>You can request the deletion or modification of your personal information by contacting us at: <a href="mailto:callu1048@gmail.com">callu1048@gmail.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>5. Updates to This Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available at this page.</p>

  <p>Thank you for trusting TopNotch Mobile with your information.</p>
